      "content": "The \"Café Shibuya\" idea sounds okay, but Marunouchi is where I really need the quiet spots to work. Can you give me 3 or 4 specific cafe recommendations actually in or very near the Marunouchi area? Also, could you break down the transit part a bit more? I'm a bit worried about the crowds at Shibuya station during rush hour and how long it actually takes to get from the platform to the street level.",
