      "content": "Thanks for the cafe list. Those look fine. One more thing—the Shibuya station part specifically. You mentioned the crowds, but I've heard the station is basically a massive, overwhelming maze of exits and levels. It seems like it would be incredibly easy to get lost or just overwhelmed by the sheer volume of people moving in every direction. Can you describe the layout or give me some advice on how to navigate that specific chaos without losing my head?",
